{
  "moduleId": "Delay",
  "notes": "LowPassFreq and HiPassFreq parameters are defined in the enum and serialized but never applied in applyEffect() - no filter objects exist in the class. They are vestigial/unimplemented. The dry/wet mix uses an overlap fader (scriptnode::faders::overlap): at mix=0.5 both dry and wet are at full volume (1.0); at extremes one fades to zero while the other stays at 1.0. The first buffer after construction is skipped entirely (skipFirstBuffer flag). DelayLine uses integer-sample delay only (no fractional interpolation) and has a built-in 1024-sample crossfade when delay time changes to prevent clicks.",
